ROS - Robot Operating System
----------------------------
ROS announcement article:
http://www.ros.org/news/2010/08/robots-using-ros-lego-nxt.html

Lego Digital Designer (LDD) support:
http://www.willowgarage.com/blog/2010/09/16/robots-using-ros-part-v-meka-qbo-mini-pr2-lego-nxt
 "Lego NXT: You can now connect Lego Mindstorms NXT robots to ROS and even
  convert models from Lego Digital Designer."
For LDD: see http://ldd.lego.com/

Using ROS with Mindstorms NXT:
http://www.ros.org/wiki/nxt

NXT-Python
----------
nxt-python is a python driver/interface for the Lego Mindstorms NXT robot.
http://code.google.com/p/nxt-python/
